sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant CLI as amplihack CLI
    participant Inst as Install Module
    participant Claude as Claude Code
    participant Hooks as Hook Runtime
    participant WF as Workflow Classifier
    participant Recipe as Recipe Runner
    participant Agent as Agent Loop
    participant Mem as Memory Store
    participant GH as GitHub API

    Note over U,GH: Journey 1: First-Time Install & Launch

    U->>CLI: amplihack install
    CLI->>Inst: commands::install::run()
    Inst->>Inst: stage amplifier-bundle
    Inst->>Inst: write hooks to .claude/
    Inst-->>CLI: install complete
    U->>CLI: amplihack launch
    CLI->>Claude: spawn claude process
    Claude->>Hooks: session_start hook
    Hooks->>WF: classify initial context
    WF-->>Hooks: Q&A workflow
    Hooks-->>Claude: session initialized

    Note over U,GH: Journey 2: Development Task via /dev

    U->>Claude: /dev "Add auth to API"
    Claude->>Hooks: user_prompt hook
    Hooks->>WF: classify task
    WF-->>Hooks: DEVELOPMENT
    Hooks->>Recipe: smart-orchestrator recipe
    Recipe->>Recipe: parse YAML steps
    Recipe->>Agent: spawn builder agent
    Agent->>Mem: get_recent_discoveries()
    Mem-->>Agent: relevant context
    Agent->>Agent: generate code
    Agent->>Mem: store_discovery()
    Agent-->>Recipe: step complete
    Recipe-->>Claude: task complete
    Claude-->>U: response with changes

    Note over U,GH: Journey 3: Recipe Execution

    U->>CLI: amplihack recipe run code-atlas.yaml
    CLI->>Recipe: executor::run()
    Recipe->>Recipe: parse + validate
    Recipe->>Agent: build layers 1-4
    Agent->>Mem: store atlas data
    Agent-->>Recipe: layers built
    Recipe->>Agent: build layers 5-8
    Agent-->>Recipe: layers built
    Recipe->>Agent: verify all layers
    Recipe->>GH: file issues (if bug hunt)
    Recipe-->>CLI: atlas complete

    Note over U,GH: Journey 4: Fleet Operations

    U->>CLI: amplihack fleet scout
    CLI->>GH: list repos
    GH-->>CLI: repo list
    CLI->>CLI: evaluate each repo
    CLI-->>U: scout report
    U->>CLI: amplihack fleet advance
    CLI->>GH: create PRs
    GH-->>CLI: PR URLs
    CLI-->>U: advancement complete

    Note over U,GH: Journey 5: Memory Query

    U->>CLI: amplihack query-code "find auth"
    CLI->>Mem: query_graph("find auth")
    Mem->>Mem: graph traversal
    Mem-->>CLI: matching nodes
    CLI-->>U: results
